TCHLYC                     MOVE A2ZETI    I2ZETI           ABSOLUTE #
TCHLYC                     MOVE PNONY     I2DELY           DELIVERY
TCHLYC*
TCHLYC* CALUCULATE THE TOTAL WEIGHT PAR PART
TCHLYC* (QTY/CONTAINER) * (FINISHED WEIGHT) = NET WEIGHT PER BOX(G)
TCHLYC* (NET WEIGHT PER BOX) / 1000      = TOTAL WEIGHT / PART(KG)
TCHLYC* TOTAL WEIGHT / PART(KG) X 2.2046 = TOTAL WEIGHT / PART(LBS)
TCHLYC* TOTAL WEIGHT / PART(LBS) + 2.3 (CONTAINER WIGHT WITHOUT PART) = TOT
TCHLYC           WSYS      MULT A2KASI    WKOT1   92
TCHLYC           WKOT1     DIV  1000      WKOT2   92
TCHLYC           WKOT2     MULT 2.2046    WKOT2     H
TCHLYC                     ADD  2.3       WKOT2
TCHLYC                     Z-ADDWKOT2     PIQTY
TCHLYC                     MOVE *BLANK    POQTY
TCHLYC                     CALL 'AB#R2K'  P2
TCHLYC                     MOVELPOQTY     I2WEIT           QTY
TCHLY *
TCHLYC                     Z-ADDWSYS      PIQTY
TCHLYC                     MOVE *BLANK    POQTY
TCHLYC                     CALL 'AB#R2K'  P2
TCHLYC                     MOVELPOQTY     I2QTY            QTY
TCHLYC*
TCHLYC                     MOVELPOQTY     I2UNIT           QTY/CONT
TCHLYC           I2SBN5    IFEQ *BLANK
TCHLYC                     MOVELBASBAN    I2SBN5
TCHLYC                     ENDIF
